      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello¡<br />\nI´m trying to connect a google sheet to Monday with Integromat.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/8/86a07fd29d5e1df9162a5be0698dbf5533688926.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/8/86a07fd29d5e1df9162a5be0698dbf5533688926_2_690x355.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"355\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1234×635 64 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Integromat receives properly data output from google sheet.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/17df2a2fac170b6a085f10ed911da26fffbd9862.png\" title=\"integromat-monday2\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/17df2a2fac170b6a085f10ed911da26fffbd9862_2_690x403.png\" alt=\"integromat-monday2\" width=\"690\" height=\"403\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">integromat-monday2</span><span class=\"informations\">1069×625 71.8 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>But between Intgromat and Monday there is an error when i´m trying to create an item in Monday with the google sheet data (it says : [200] There are items that are not in the connected boards [ Error Code: ColumnValueException / Error Details: {} ]<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/7/7a95352f622b93aec685235ea64f5b049f78dbda.png\" title=\"integromat-monday3\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/7/7a95352f622b93aec685235ea64f5b049f78dbda_2_690x445.png\" alt=\"integromat-monday3\" width=\"690\" height=\"445\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">integromat-monday3</span><span class=\"informations\">1013×654 71.8 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/d1e181bb4dec1af2a30387c1bc8519ae37f74e53.png\" title=\"integromat-monday4\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/d1e181bb4dec1af2a30387c1bc8519ae37f74e53_2_690x408.png\" alt=\"integromat-monday4\" width=\"690\" height=\"408\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">integromat-monday4</span><span class=\"informations\">1064×630 76.4 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Any clue to solve it?<br />\nThanks a lot.</p>"
